{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"It sure used to be a lot easier to be from Iceland,"},{"time":3000,"text":"because until a couple of years ago,"},{"time":5000,"text":"people knew hardly anything about us,"},{"time":7000,"text":"and I could basically come out here"},{"time":9000,"text":"and say only good things about us."},{"time":11000,"text":"But in the last couple of years"},{"time":13000,"text":"we've become infamous for a couple of things."},{"time":16000,"text":"First, of course, the economic meltdown."},{"time":19000,"text":"It actually got so bad"},{"time":21000,"text":"that somebody put our country up for sale on eBay."},{"time":24000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":26000,"text":"Ninety-nine pence was the starting price"},{"time":28000,"text":"and no reserve."},{"time":31000,"text":"Then there was the volcano"},{"time":33000,"text":"that interrupted the travel plans"},{"time":35000,"text":"of almost all of you and many of your friends,"},{"time":38000,"text":"including President Obama."},{"time":40000,"text":"By the way, the pronunciation"},{"time":42000,"text":"is \"Eyjafjallajokull.\""},{"time":44000,"text":"None of your media got it right."}]},{"cues":[{"time":46000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":48000,"text":"But I'm not here to share these stories"},{"time":50000,"text":"about these two things exactly."},{"time":52000,"text":"I'm here to tell you the story of Audur Capital,"},{"time":54000,"text":"which is a financial firm founded by me"},{"time":56000,"text":"and Kristin -- who you see in the picture --"},{"time":58000,"text":"in the spring of 2007,"},{"time":61000,"text":"just over a year before the economic collapse hit."},{"time":64000,"text":"Why would two women"},{"time":66000,"text":"who were enjoying successful careers in investment banking"},{"time":68000,"text":"in the corporate sector"},{"time":70000,"text":"leave to found a financial services firm?"},{"time":73000,"text":"Well let it suffice to say"},{"time":76000,"text":"that we felt a bit overwhelmed"},{"time":79000,"text":"with testosterone."},{"time":81000,"text":"And I'm not here to say"},{"time":83000,"text":"that men are to blame for the crisis"},{"time":85000,"text":"and what happened in my country."},{"time":87000,"text":"But I can surely tell you that in my country,"},{"time":89000,"text":"much like on Wall Street and the city of London and elsewhere,"},{"time":92000,"text":"men were at the helm"},{"time":94000,"text":"of the game of the financial sector,"},{"time":96000,"text":"and that kind of lack of diversity"},{"time":99000,"text":"and sameness"},{"time":101000,"text":"leads to disastrous problems."}]},{"cues":[{"time":103000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":106000,"text":"So we decided, a bit fed-up with this world"},{"time":109000,"text":"and also with the strong feeling in our stomach"},{"time":112000,"text":"that this wasn't sustainable,"},{"time":114000,"text":"to found a financial services firm"},{"time":116000,"text":"based on our values,"},{"time":119000,"text":"and we decided to incorporate feminine values"},{"time":122000,"text":"into the world of finance."},{"time":124000,"text":"Raised quite a few eyebrows in Iceland."},{"time":126000,"text":"We weren't known"},{"time":128000,"text":"as the typical \"women\" women"},{"time":130000,"text":"in Iceland up until then."},{"time":132000,"text":"So it was almost like coming out of the closet"},{"time":135000,"text":"to actually talk about the fact that we were women"},{"time":137000,"text":"and that we believed that we had a set of values"},{"time":139000,"text":"and a way of doing business"},{"time":142000,"text":"that would be more sustainable"},{"time":144000,"text":"than what we had experienced until then."},{"time":148000,"text":"And we got a great group of people to join us --"},{"time":150000,"text":"principled people with great skills,"},{"time":153000,"text":"and investors with a vision"},{"time":155000,"text":"and values to match ours."},{"time":157000,"text":"And together we got through the eye of the financial storm in Iceland"},{"time":160000,"text":"without taking any direct losses to our equity"},{"time":163000,"text":"or to the funds of our clients."},{"time":165000,"text":"And although I want to thank"},{"time":167000,"text":"the talented people of our company"},{"time":169000,"text":"foremost for that --"},{"time":171000,"text":"and also there's a factor of luck and timing --"},{"time":174000,"text":"we are absolutely convinced"},{"time":176000,"text":"that we did this because of our values."}]},{"cues":[{"time":179000,"text":"So let me share with you our values."},{"time":182000,"text":"We believe in risk awareness."},{"time":184000,"text":"What does that mean?"},{"time":186000,"text":"We believe that you should always understand the risks that you're taking,"},{"time":189000,"text":"and we will not invest"},{"time":191000,"text":"in things we don't understand."},{"time":193000,"text":"Not a complicated thing."},{"time":195000,"text":"But in 2007,"},{"time":197000,"text":"at the height of the sub-prime"},{"time":200000,"text":"and all the complicated financial structures,"},{"time":202000,"text":"it was quite opposite"},{"time":204000,"text":"to the reckless risk-taking behaviors"},{"time":207000,"text":"that we saw on the market."},{"time":209000,"text":"We also believe in straight-talking,"},{"time":211000,"text":"telling it as it is,"},{"time":213000,"text":"using simple language that people understand,"},{"time":216000,"text":"telling people about the downsides"},{"time":218000,"text":"as well as the potential upsides,"},{"time":221000,"text":"and even telling the bad news that no one wants to utter,"},{"time":224000,"text":"like our lack of belief in the sustainability"},{"time":226000,"text":"of the Icelandic financial sector"},{"time":228000,"text":"that already we had"},{"time":230000,"text":"months before the collapse hit us."},{"time":232000,"text":"And, although we do work in the financial sector,"},{"time":235000,"text":"where Excel is king,"},{"time":237000,"text":"we believe in emotional capital."},{"time":240000,"text":"And we believe"},{"time":242000,"text":"that doing emotional due diligence"},{"time":244000,"text":"is just as important"},{"time":246000,"text":"as doing financial due diligence."},{"time":250000,"text":"It is actually people"},{"time":252000,"text":"that make money and lose money,"},{"time":254000,"text":"not Excel spreadsheets."}]},{"cues":[{"time":258000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":260000,"text":"Last, but not least,"},{"time":262000,"text":"we believe in profit with principles."},{"time":264000,"text":"We care how we make our profit."},{"time":266000,"text":"So while we want to make economic profit for ourselves and our customers,"},{"time":269000,"text":"we are willing to do it with a long-term view,"},{"time":272000,"text":"and we like to have a wider definition of profits"},{"time":275000,"text":"than just the economic profit in the next quarter."},{"time":278000,"text":"So we like to see profits,"},{"time":280000,"text":"plus positive social"},{"time":282000,"text":"and environmental benefits, when we invest."}]},{"cues":[{"time":285000,"text":"But it wasn't just about the values,"},{"time":287000,"text":"although we are convinced that they matter."},{"time":289000,"text":"It was also about a business opportunity."},{"time":291000,"text":"It's the female trend, and it's the sustainability trend,"},{"time":294000,"text":"that are going to create"},{"time":296000,"text":"some of the most interesting investment opportunities"},{"time":298000,"text":"in the years to come."},{"time":300000,"text":"The whole thing about the female trend"},{"time":302000,"text":"is not about women being better than men;"},{"time":304000,"text":"it is actually about"},{"time":306000,"text":"women being different from men,"},{"time":308000,"text":"bringing different values and different ways to the table."},{"time":311000,"text":"So what do you get? You get better decision-making,"},{"time":314000,"text":"and you get less herd behavior,"},{"time":316000,"text":"and both of those things hit your bottom line"},{"time":319000,"text":"with very positive results."}]},{"cues":[{"time":322000,"text":"But one has to wonder,"},{"time":324000,"text":"now that we've had this financial sector collapse upon us in Iceland --"},{"time":327000,"text":"and by the way, Europe looks pretty bad right now,"},{"time":330000,"text":"and many would say that you in America"},{"time":332000,"text":"are heading for some more trouble as well."},{"time":335000,"text":"Now that we've had all that happen,"},{"time":337000,"text":"and we have all this data out there"},{"time":339000,"text":"telling us that it's much better to have diversity"},{"time":341000,"text":"around the decision-making tables,"},{"time":343000,"text":"will we see business and finance change?"},{"time":346000,"text":"Will government change?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":348000,"text":"Well I'll give you my straight talk about this."},{"time":351000,"text":"I have days that I believe,"},{"time":353000,"text":"but I have days that I'm full of doubt."},{"time":356000,"text":"Have you seen the incredible urge out there"},{"time":359000,"text":"to rebuild the very things that failed us?"},{"time":362000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":364000,"text":"Einstein said"},{"time":366000,"text":"that this was the definition of insanity --"},{"time":369000,"text":"to do the same things"},{"time":371000,"text":"over and over again,"},{"time":373000,"text":"hoping for a different outcome."},{"time":376000,"text":"So I guess the world is insane,"},{"time":378000,"text":"because I see entirely too much"},{"time":380000,"text":"of doing the same things over and over again,"},{"time":383000,"text":"hoping that this time it's not going to collapse upon us."},{"time":386000,"text":"I want to see more revolutionary thinking,"},{"time":389000,"text":"and I remain hopeful."},{"time":391000,"text":"Like TED, I believe in people."},{"time":393000,"text":"And I know that consumers"},{"time":395000,"text":"are becoming more conscious,"},{"time":397000,"text":"and they are going to start voting with their wallets,"},{"time":400000,"text":"and they are going to change the face"},{"time":402000,"text":"of business and finance from the outside,"},{"time":404000,"text":"if they don't do it from the inside."}]},{"cues":[{"time":407000,"text":"But I'm more of the revolutionary,"},{"time":410000,"text":"and I should be; I'm from Iceland."},{"time":412000,"text":"We have a long history"},{"time":414000,"text":"of strong, courageous, independent women,"},{"time":417000,"text":"ever since the Viking age."},{"time":419000,"text":"And I want to tell you when"},{"time":421000,"text":"I first realized that women matter to the economy"},{"time":423000,"text":"and to the society,"},{"time":425000,"text":"I was seven -- it happened to be my mother's birthday --"},{"time":427000,"text":"October 24, 1975."},{"time":430000,"text":"Women in Iceland took the day off."},{"time":433000,"text":"From work or from home, they took the day off,"},{"time":436000,"text":"and nothing worked in Iceland."},{"time":438000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":441000,"text":"They marched into the center of Reykjavik,"},{"time":443000,"text":"and they put women's issues onto the agenda."},{"time":446000,"text":"And some say this was the start of a global movement."},{"time":449000,"text":"For me it was the start of a long journey,"},{"time":452000,"text":"but I decided that day to matter."},{"time":455000,"text":"Five years later,"},{"time":457000,"text":"Iceland elected Vigdis Finnbogadottir as their president --"},{"time":460000,"text":"first female to become head of state,"},{"time":463000,"text":"single mom,"},{"time":465000,"text":"a breast cancer survivor"},{"time":467000,"text":"who had had one of her breasts removed."},{"time":469000,"text":"And at one of the campaign sessions,"},{"time":471000,"text":"she had one of her male contenders"},{"time":474000,"text":"allude to the fact that she couldn't become president --"},{"time":476000,"text":"she was a woman, and even half a woman."},{"time":480000,"text":"That night she won the election,"},{"time":482000,"text":"because she came back --"},{"time":484000,"text":"not just because of his crappy behavior --"},{"time":487000,"text":"but she came back and said,"},{"time":490000,"text":"\"Well, I'm actually not going to breastfeed the Icelandic nation;"},{"time":493000,"text":"I'm going to lead it.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":495000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":499000,"text":"So I've had incredibly many"},{"time":502000,"text":"women role models"},{"time":504000,"text":"that have influenced who I am and where I am today."},{"time":506000,"text":"But in spite of that,"},{"time":508000,"text":"I went through the first 10 or 15 years of my career"},{"time":510000,"text":"mostly in denial of being a woman."},{"time":513000,"text":"Started in corporate America,"},{"time":515000,"text":"and I was absolutely convinced"},{"time":517000,"text":"that it was just about the individual,"},{"time":519000,"text":"that women and men would have just the same opportunities."},{"time":522000,"text":"But I've come to conclude lately"},{"time":524000,"text":"that it isn't like that."},{"time":526000,"text":"We are not the same,"},{"time":528000,"text":"and it's great. Because of our differences,"},{"time":530000,"text":"we create and sustain life."},{"time":532000,"text":"So we should embrace our difference and aim for challenge."}]},{"cues":[{"time":535000,"text":"The final thought I want to leave with you"},{"time":537000,"text":"is that I'm fed up with this tyranny"},{"time":539000,"text":"of either/or choices in life --"},{"time":541000,"text":"either it's men or it's women."},{"time":544000,"text":"We need to start embracing the beauty of balance."},{"time":547000,"text":"So let's move away"},{"time":549000,"text":"from thinking about business here and philanthropy there,"},{"time":552000,"text":"and let's start thinking about"},{"time":554000,"text":"doing good business."},{"time":556000,"text":"That's how we change the world. That's the only sustainable future."}]},{"cues":[{"time":559000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":561000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}